text: Enzo Sanga (born 19 May 1995) is a French rugby union footballer. He plays as a scrum-half. Born in Vichy, Enzo Sanga currently plays for Montpellier Herault RC in the Top 14. ==References== ==External links== *ESPN Profile *itsrugby.co.uk Profile Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:French rugby union players Category:Montpellier Hérault Rugby players Category:Rugby union scrum-halves Category:People from Vichy Category:Sportspeople from Allier
